    <li><a title="#xarML('Xaraya Twitter Module')#" href="http://crispcreations.co.uk/xar/mods/twitter"><xar:mlstring>Twitter Module home page</xar:mlstring></a> <xar:mlstring> at CrispCreations</xar:mlstring>
    </li>
    <li><xar:mlstring>Twitter Extension page at</xar:mlstring> <a title="#xarML('Twitter Module - Xaraya Extension 991')#" href="http://www.xaraya.com/index.php/release/991.html"><xar:mlstring>Xaraya Extension and Releases</xar:mlstring></a>.
      <xar:mlstring> Click on Version History tab at the bottom to get the latest release information.</xar:mlstring>
    </li>
    <li><xar:mlstring>Related tutorials and documentation on Twitter Module found at</xar:mlstring> <a href="http://www.xaraya.com/index.php/keywords/twitter/" title="#xarML('Related documentation on Twitter')#"><xar:mlstring>Xaraya Documentation.</xar:mlstring></a>
